  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can touch a creature as a standard action to suppress its strong emotions. The target is affected as the&nbsp;calm emotions&nbsp;spell, except it can still take violent actions and violent actions against the target do not end the effect. This effect lasts a number of rounds equal to 1/2 your cleric level (minimum 1). You can use this ability a number times per day equal to 3 + your Wisdom modifier.</p>\n<p>This power replaces the Icicle power of the Water Domain.</p>"
